      "content": "but its not just \"noise\" though. it's not a sound i can actually hear with my ears, i feel it in my bones. like a physical throb. and the timing is so weird... it only happens when they are active. like, i'll be sitting there and suddenly i just feel this wave of pure irritability and my heart starts racing. it feels way too coordinated to be just random household stuff. don't you think it's possible there's tech that can do this?",
